{"tid":779392,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《漫威制裁者》第二季拍攝完成！眾星齊聚殺青派對狂歡","createTime":"2018-08-14T11:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T13:42:33.000Z","uid":49391,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d050181439c517f1cd4cbb683a8a9616fc6a1250","tid":779392,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/190700_61ea0dbb78b983e0b0e66b20ae4a7319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F190700_61ea0dbb78b983e0b0e66b20ae4a7319.jpg&h=ab9cfce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歷經多月拍攝後，Netflix 美劇《漫威制裁者》（Marvel's The Punisher）第二季日前殺青！眾演員在 Instagram 上發布多張合照，曝光殺青派對的歡樂模樣。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n劇中飾演退伍軍人的男星傑森&middot;R&middot;摩爾（Jason R. Moore）上傳與導演傑瑞米韋柏（Jeremy Webb）、主演強柏恩瑟（Jon Bernthal）的合照，向粉絲宣布第二季殺青。<br />\n首季演出國安局探員的女星安柏蘿絲瑞瓦（Amber Rose Revah）、在《漫威夜魔俠》中首度登場的探員男星羅伊斯約翰遜（Royce Johnson）也上傳多張殺青派對的照片。幕前、幕後人員大齊聚，開心的一同入鏡合照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/190746_1637de96c5e620bcebc7ffcc67a43a45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F190746_1637de96c5e620bcebc7ffcc67a43a45.jpg&h=906e7154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《漫威制裁者》第二季尚未公布上線日期，不過由於接下來 9 月 7 日將推出《漫威鐵拳俠》（Marvel's Iron Fist）第二季，《漫威夜魔俠》（Marvel's Daredevil）第三季也確定會在今年底前上線。因此，《漫威制裁者》第二季被推測應是 2019 年才會回歸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/190801_a118f00895debbd677fcb2552f2bb85f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F190801_a118f00895debbd677fcb2552f2bb85f.jpg&h=0afacda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該劇先前曝光多組片場照和影片，證實首季參演男星班巴恩斯（Ben Barnes）回歸，繼續重拾比利羅素（Billy Russo）一角。新加盟演員則有《驚聲尖叫》女星喬姬雅惠格姆（Giorgia Whigham）、《狙擊生死線》喬許史都華（Josh Stewart）、《女超人》芙芮娜莉瑪（Floriana Lima）、《靈異妙探》科賓本森（Corbin Bernsen）以及《超人前傳(2001)》安妮特奧圖（Annette O&rsquo;Toole）。（mcuexchange）"},{"pid":"ec4a627772fb6596fc4e7a33d4a5b16d1bdc4125","tid":779392,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"想扮大片拍水準又未夠"},{"pid":"833e487a4b61d7e13df81cf9e8b7ef3f68c8f39e","tid":779392,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"殺乜撚嘢青"},{"pid":"2aa3ecfc9a1f2f3c385b350093689273666dfb8d","tid":779392,"uid":18697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"833e487a4b61d7e13df81cf9e8b7ef3f68c8f39e","tid":779392,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"殺乜撚嘢青"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"製茶其中一個工序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7357c6fc7653f8f44e208cf393d5adcc45d913","tid":779392,"uid":137569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"833e487a4b61d7e13df81cf9e8b7ef3f68c8f39e","tid":779392,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"殺乜撚嘢青"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"又想屌蝗語呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f40a0700ff1b8f44fb9e5334ece1a1eb54c71","tid":779392,"uid":197222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"Netflix Marvel series剩返Punisher最值得期待 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60d9b565812a12e3fa40c7d6ae39c92b7503802","tid":779392,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"1c7357c6fc7653f8f44e208cf393d5adcc45d913","tid":779392,"uid":137569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"833e487a4b61d7e13df81cf9e8b7ef3f68c8f39e","tid":779392,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"殺乜撚嘢青"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"又想屌蝗語呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"